solution:
We can determine the other two angles in the triangle with the unknown angle.  Label its vertices $X$, $Y$, and $Z$.

[asy]
import markers; defaultpen(linewidth(0.8));

pair A,B,C,D,EE,F,G;

draw(unitcircle);

A=(-1,0);
B=(0,-1);
C=(1,0);
D=(0,1);

draw(A--B--C--D--A);

EE=(-0.9,-0.45);
F=(0.9,-0.45);

